00:10:21.287 --> 00:10:24.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
それに そろそろ
食料を補給しねえとな

137
00:10:24.665 --> 00:10:27.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
この前の町じゃ
何も蓄えてねえ

138
00:10:27.501 --> 00:10:29.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あそこに河口が見えるぜ

139
00:10:30.087 --> 00:10:31.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（サンジ）え？
（ナミ）えっ ホント？

140
00:10:36.719 --> 00:10:38.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（ルフィ）
焼肉屋あるといいな

141
00:10:38.429 --> 00:10:39.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（サンジ）
んなもんがあるか

142
00:10:39.847 --> 00:10:42.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（ルフィ）
だって 言ったろ？
“食料を補給する”って

143
00:10:42.350 --> 00:10:46.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（サンジ）
材料を集めるんだ
…ったく何 考えてんだ てめえは

144
00:10:46.646 --> 00:10:48.522 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（ナミ）
でも 上陸は危険だわ

145
00:10:51.359 --> 00:10:52.568 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
大体 見てよ

146
00:10:52.693 --> 00:10:56.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
こんな植物
私 図鑑でも見たことないわ

147
00:10:56.572 --> 00:10:59.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（鳥の鳴き声）

148
00:11:00.117 --> 00:11:01.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（ナミ）キャアッ
（ウソップ）わあっ

149
00:11:02.286 --> 00:11:05.039 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あ… かわいい…

150
00:11:05.665 --> 00:11:06.624 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
俺か？

151
00:11:06.749 --> 00:11:09.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ナミさんに決まってんだろ

152
00:11:09.251 --> 00:11:10.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
今の何なの？

153
00:11:12.755 --> 00:11:15.341 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
大丈夫さ　ただの鳥だよ

154
00:11:15.466 --> 00:11:17.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
そして ここは
ただのジャングル

155
00:11:17.468 --> 00:11:18.260 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
心配ねえ

156
00:11:18.511 --> 00:11:19.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（２人のおびえる声）

157
00:11:19.845 --> 00:11:22.014 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ん？ どうした？

158
00:11:22.848 --> 00:11:24.016 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ああっ

159
00:11:28.145 --> 00:11:30.231 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
何しやがる このクソ鳥

160
00:11:30.815 --> 00:11:33.150 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
トカゲか？ うめえのかな

161
00:11:33.317 --> 00:11:36.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（爆発音）

162
00:11:38.030 --> 00:11:42.034 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
これが ただのジャングルから
聞こえてくる音なの？

163
00:11:42.159 --> 00:11:46.497 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
まるで 火山でも
噴火したような音だぜ 今のは

164
00:12:05.474 --> 00:12:08.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（虎のうなり声）

165
00:12:14.275 --> 00:12:14.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
虎？

166
00:12:14.984 --> 00:12:17.361 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（ウソップ）
あーっ でかすぎる

167
00:12:17.486 --> 00:12:18.529 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ひいっ

168
00:12:20.614 --> 00:12:21.157 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
うわっ

169
00:12:27.121 --> 00:12:29.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
何？ 何があったの？

170
00:12:30.040 --> 00:12:32.460 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
普通じゃないわ
絶対 普通じゃない

171
00:12:33.294 --> 00:12:35.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
なんで ジャングルの
王者の虎が―

172
00:12:35.421 --> 00:12:37.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
血まみれで倒れるの

173
00:12:38.174 --> 00:12:43.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
うん　あっ この島には
上陸しないことに決定

174
00:12:44.138 --> 00:12:46.932 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
船の上で ログがたまるのを
静かに待って―

175
00:12:47.099 --> 00:12:47.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ウソップ）そう

176
00:12:47.766 --> 00:12:49.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
一刻も早く
この島を出ましょう

177
00:12:49.852 --> 00:12:50.811 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ウソップ）そう

178
00:12:52.062 --> 00:12:54.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
早くアラバスタへ
行かなきゃね

179
00:12:54.482 --> 00:12:55.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ゾロ）よっ…

180
00:13:04.283 --> 00:13:07.203 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（ルフィ）
ニヒヒヒヒヒヒッ

181
00:13:07.328 --> 00:13:09.079 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
サンジ 弁当

182
00:13:09.205 --> 00:13:09.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
弁当？

183
00:13:10.664 --> 00:13:12.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（ルフィ）
ああ パワー補給だ

184
00:13:12.666 --> 00:13:16.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
肉いっぱいの
野菜抜きの海賊弁当

185
00:13:16.337 --> 00:13:17.922 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
冒険のにおいがする

186
00:13:18.756 --> 00:13:22.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ちょっ… ちょっと待ってよ あんた
どこ行くつもり？

187
00:13:22.468 --> 00:13:26.597 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
冒険　ウッヒヒ
来るか？ 冒険 冒険

188
00:13:27.348 --> 00:13:30.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（ナミ）
ダメだ 止まらない
いきいきしすぎ

189
00:13:31.101 --> 00:13:36.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（ウソップ）
ウソだろ？ 大虎ふっ飛ばす
バケモンがいるんだぞ

190
00:13:36.440 --> 00:13:38.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
サンジ　弁当

191
00:13:38.609 --> 00:13:41.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
分かったよ
ちょっと待ってろ

192
00:13:41.445 --> 00:13:43.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（ルフィ）
イヒヒッ イヒヒヒヒ

193
00:13:44.448 --> 00:13:46.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ねえ 私も一緒に行っていい？

194
00:13:47.034 --> 00:13:47.785 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
えーっ

195
00:13:47.910 --> 00:13:49.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
おう　来い来い

196
00:13:49.495 --> 00:13:51.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あんたまで何 言うの

197
00:13:51.705 --> 00:13:55.668 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ええ　じっとしてたら
いろいろ考えちゃいそうだし

198
00:13:56.043 --> 00:13:58.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ログがたまるまで 気晴らしに

199
00:13:58.295 --> 00:13:59.004 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
そんな

200
00:13:59.129 --> 00:14:01.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
ルフィはともかく
あなたには危険すぎるわ

201
00:14:02.383 --> 00:14:04.885 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
大丈夫よ カルーがいるから

202
00:14:05.719 --> 00:14:07.221 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（カルー）アアーッ

203
00:14:08.055 --> 00:14:11.559 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
本人 言葉にならないくらい
驚いてるけど

204
00:14:11.850 --> 00:14:14.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
じゃあ ビビちゃんに
愛情弁当を

205
00:14:15.187 --> 00:14:17.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
カルーに ドリンクも
お願いできる？

206
00:14:18.065 --> 00:14:20.985 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
もちろん　お任せください

207
00:14:26.574 --> 00:14:27.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（サンジ）よし
（ルフィ）ヒヒヒッ

208
00:14:33.372 --> 00:14:37.501 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
さあ 海賊弁当２丁に
カルー用の特製ドリンク

209
00:14:37.626 --> 00:14:39.044 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
すべて入ったぜ

210
00:14:39.211 --> 00:14:40.087 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
うん

211
00:14:40.504 --> 00:14:41.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
よっと

212
00:14:41.922 --> 00:14:42.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ハッ

213
00:14:45.009 --> 00:14:45.551 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ビビ）じゃあ

214
00:14:45.968 --> 00:14:47.261 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
行ってくるわね

215
00:14:47.595 --> 00:14:48.929 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ルフィ）おし 行くぞ！

216
00:14:49.054 --> 00:14:51.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
おおよそで戻ってくるから

217
00:14:52.683 --> 00:14:55.811 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
度胸あるな ミス･ウェンズデー

218
00:14:56.228 --> 00:14:59.231 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
さすが 敵の会社に
潜入するだけあるわ

219
00:15:02.359 --> 00:15:04.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
じゃあ 俺も暇だし
散歩してくる

220
00:15:05.070 --> 00:15:06.113 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
散歩？

221
00:15:06.864 --> 00:15:08.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ゾロ）あーらよっ

222
00:15:10.576 --> 00:15:12.244 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あっ おい ゾロ

223
00:15:12.912 --> 00:15:13.954 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
待て待て

224
00:15:14.079 --> 00:15:14.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ゾロ）ん？

225
00:15:15.414 --> 00:15:17.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
食料が足りねんだ

226
00:15:17.291 --> 00:15:19.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
食えそうな獣でもいたら
捕ってきてくれ

227
00:15:20.252 --> 00:15:21.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ああ 分かった

228
00:15:22.171 --> 00:15:24.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
お前じゃ 到底
しとめられそうにねえやつを―

229
00:15:24.590 --> 00:15:26.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
捕ってきてやるよ

230
00:15:26.425 --> 00:15:27.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（サンジ）待て コラーッ！

231
00:15:28.135 --> 00:15:29.219 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ゾロ）ああ？

232
00:15:29.929 --> 00:15:31.805 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（サンジ）聞き捨てならねえ

233
00:15:32.264 --> 00:15:36.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
てめえが 俺よりでけえ獲物を
狩ってこられるだと？

234
00:15:37.811 --> 00:15:38.979 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
当然だろ

235
00:15:44.693 --> 00:15:45.903 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
狩り勝負だ

236
00:15:49.865 --> 00:15:53.035 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
いいか
肉 何キロ取れたか勝負！

237
00:15:53.535 --> 00:15:55.204 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
何トンかの間違いだろ

238
00:15:55.621 --> 00:15:58.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（サンジ）
獲物を並べてから
ごたくも並べな

239
00:15:58.165 --> 00:16:00.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（ゾロ）
フンッ　望むところだ

240
00:16:01.961 --> 00:16:03.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
どいつもこいつも

241
00:16:03.295 --> 00:16:05.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
なんで あいつら
あんなに こうなのかしら

242
00:16:05.714 --> 00:16:07.383 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
分かるぜ その気持ち

243
00:16:07.508 --> 00:16:10.135 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
泣くな
俺は おめえの味方だよ

244
00:16:10.260 --> 00:16:14.390 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（鳥の鳴き声）

245
00:16:14.515 --> 00:16:15.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（２人）あっ

246
00:16:16.141 --> 00:16:17.101 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
頼りねえ

247
00:16:17.226 --> 00:16:19.478 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
それは 私のセリフよ

248
00:16:20.020 --> 00:16:21.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（２人）ハアーッ

249
00:16:22.272 --> 00:16:23.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ナミ）うーん

250
00:16:24.024 --> 00:16:25.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
でも ちょっと待って

251
00:16:26.527 --> 00:16:27.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
え？ あっ どど… どうした？

252
00:16:30.072 --> 00:16:31.949 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あだだだ… ナミ？

253
00:16:32.157 --> 00:16:33.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ナミ）これじゃない

254
00:16:33.283 --> 00:16:34.827 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
うーん これも違う

255
00:16:34.952 --> 00:16:35.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あたっ 痛(いて)っ イタイタ…

256
00:16:36.078 --> 00:16:37.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
おっ おい ナミ ナミ

257
00:16:37.913 --> 00:16:40.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
おい 一体 何 捜してんだよ

258
00:16:40.249 --> 00:16:42.710 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（ナミ）
何か 本で読んだ
記憶があるのよ

259
00:16:43.168 --> 00:16:45.129 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ウソップ）な… 何をだ

260
00:16:45.254 --> 00:16:46.755 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ナミ）リトルガーデン

261
00:16:48.757 --> 00:16:49.717 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ルフィ）ヘヘヘヘヘッ

262
00:16:49.842 --> 00:16:51.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（カルーの鳴き声）

263
00:16:51.385 --> 00:16:53.262 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ルフィ）よーっとととーっ

264
00:16:53.762 --> 00:16:54.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ヘヘヘッ

265
00:16:55.097 --> 00:16:55.764 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
どうしたの？

266
00:16:55.889 --> 00:16:57.182 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ほら これ見ろよ

267
00:16:57.808 --> 00:16:59.810 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
イカみたいな貝がいるぞ

268
00:17:03.647 --> 00:17:04.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（ルフィ）イカガイ？

269
00:17:05.524 --> 00:17:08.527 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
これって
アンモナイトによく似てる

270
00:17:08.652 --> 00:17:09.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
イカ貝だろ

271
00:17:09.611 --> 00:17:13.490 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（大きな物音）

272
00:17:13.741 --> 00:17:15.117 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（２人）ん？
（カルー）ワアッ

273
00:17:21.874 --> 00:17:25.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
さっきから 誰か
後をつけてるような

274
00:17:25.252 --> 00:17:26.462 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
まっ 気のせいか

275
00:17:35.679 --> 00:17:36.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
んっ

276
00:17:41.727 --> 00:17:42.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
おっと

277
