00:18:29.566 --> 00:18:30.609 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
恐竜？

286
00:18:30.901 --> 00:18:33.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
